	(251,1,'2018-12-03 20:38:03','2018-12-03 20:38:03','We are the plant pushers – your partners in everyday wellness. We create affordable, super tasty plant-based food that goes big on nutrition and even bigger on flavour. Our wholesome dishes are completely free from guilt. No additives. No nasties. Just real food.\r\n\r\nWhat you eat directly affects how you feel. It’s hardly rocket science. It’s plain common sense. The global shift towards better nutrition no fleeting fad. It didn’t happen overnight. It’s a sign that we know more than ever about what keeps us healthy. The more we learn, the more power we have to take control and give our body’s what they need most.\r\n<h2>Excite</h2>\r\nExperience a completely new type of food. We’re on a mission to create 100% plant-based eats that pack a real flavour punch and excite your taste buds. Experimenting with tastes from far and wide, we settle for nothing less than the most thrilling and surprising combinations.\r\n<h2>Nourish</h2>\r\nReady to supercharge your day-to-day diet? Don’t let all the noise and misinformation confuse you. There’s one simple rule that all modern healthy eating plans have in common: Eat more plants. Done. Our plant-based eats are as nourishing as they are full of flavour. Recover, refuel, replenish yourself with every single bite.\r\n<h2>Inspire</h2>\r\nPlant-based. Vegetarian. Flexitarian. It doesn’t matter where you start, we’re here for you. We want to be by your side each step of the way. We want to empower you to live your best life and that starts with the food you choose to eat. The plant pushers are here to inform, educate, and inspire. Let’s start our journey into health together.','Our Story','','inherit','closed','closed','','125-revision-v1','','','2018-12-03 20:38:03','2018-12-03 20:38:03','',125,'http://eatshed.local/125-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(252,1,'2018-12-03 20:39:06','2018-12-03 20:39:06','<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Join the plant-based movement. We don’t just want to nourish you; we want to help you nourish yourself. From unique educational talks to recipe demonstrations, we offer a variety of events that will help you on your journey. </span>','Events','','inherit','closed','closed','','10-revision-v1','','','2018-12-03 20:39:06','2018-12-03 20:39:06','',10,'http://eatshed.local/10-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
